+// ********************************************************************************************************************
+// The following snippets are adapted from the original work of Yafay and Altingovde
+// https://github.com/yfy-/Quant-BM-WAND/blob/master/src/lowerbound_threshold.cpp
+// Caching Scores for Faster Query Processing with Dynamic Pruning in Search Engines
+// CIKM 2019
